I"5<h2 id="prerequisites">Prerequisites</h2>

<ol>
  <li>Need to have a valid ZOHO CRM account.</li>
</ol>

<h2 id="steps-to-add-new-customeraccounts-in-priority">Steps to add new Customer/Accounts in Priority</h2>

<ol>
  <li>Login to the ZOHO CRM cloud portal. The home page of the ZOHO CRM can be viewed below.</li>
</ol>

<p><img src="/staticfiles/connectors/media/application-connector/zohocrm-addaccount1.png" alt="zohocrm-addaccount1" /></p>

<ol>
  <li>Navigate to the menu ACCOUNTS in the home page for adding new customers.</li>
</ol>

<p><img src="/staticfiles/connectors/media/application-connector/zohocrm-addaccount2.png" alt="zohocrm-addaccount2" /></p>
<ol>
  <li>On clicking Accounts, the account window opens up. Click on the + symbol to add a new Account/Customer in ZOHO CRM.</li>
</ol>

<p><img src="/staticfiles/connectors/media/application-connector/zohocrm-addaccount3.png" alt="zohocrm-addaccount3" /></p>
<ol>
  <li>Fill up the details in the form that opens up.</li>
</ol>

<p><img src="/staticfiles/connectors/media/application-connector/zohocrm-addaccount4.png" alt="zohocrm-addaccount4" /></p>

<p><img src="/staticfiles/connectors/media/application-connector/zohocrm-addaccount5.png" alt="zohocrm-addaccount5" /></p>
<ol>
  <li>Once done with filling up the details, click on the SAVE Button.</li>
</ol>

